# =============================================================================
# Libre Tiles — Environment Variables Overview
# =============================================================================
#
# This project has TWO environment files:
#
#   backend/.env           — Django settings (DB, secrets, CORS)
#   frontend/.env.local    — Next.js settings (AI Gateway, API URL)
#
# Quick setup:
#
#   cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
#   cp frontend/.env.local.example frontend/.env.local
#
# Then edit both files with your values.
# Or just run: ./scripts/libretiles.sh (auto-creates from examples)
#
# See backend/.env.example and frontend/.env.local.example for details.
# =============================================================================
